Url scheme

/blog/
	-> all posts, a page at a time
/blog/post/<the-post-slug>/
	-> individual
/blog/category/<the-category-slug>
	-> post *headings* as links, only
/blog/category/
	-> all categories listed

/blog/atom/
	-> atom feed for posts
/blog/atom/category/<the-category-slug>/
        -> atom feed for posts of that category

/blog/atom/comments/
	-> atom feed for all comments
/blog/atom/comments/<the-post-slug>/
        -> atom feed for comments for a post

